# Lock Files Configuration
# - uv.lock: Committed (ensures reproducible Python builds)
# - Cargo.lock: Root workspace lock committed (covers syntek-dev binary + all crates)
# - pnpm-lock.yaml: Ignored for library packages (consumers resolve their own deps)
pnpm-lock.yaml

